attributes.title: this ✨sucks✨
attributes.review: this app is terrible. i got the app to support our 🧚amazing🧚 president ✨king bernie✨and i opened the app to see an    🍊orange🍊 racist bunker boy.  after i got past the ✨ugly✨ bamboons face the app told me to inject bleach and kill myself. it was supposed to let me choose a name but before had me choose my gender. i put female and instead of letting me choose my name it automatically gave me the name, “property” it then continued to say sexist things like, “go make me a sand which” and “repeal the 19th.” the face on the front of the app is absolutely ✨mortifying✨ and it just gets worse and worse. i continued to explore the app and two options popped up. the two options were, “republican” or “democrat” and i pressed democrat and the app hypnotized me and automatically ordered me $32,000,500 in trump merch. after they hypnotize you and spends millions of dollar on ✨bunker boys✨ merch it shows a list of people part of a cult called, “conservatives.” because i was hypnotized i kept having reoccurring  nightmares of trumps speeches. it was horrifying. i then deleted the app because of my bad experiences. i now have to pay for therapy. it is $150 an hour because my therapist has to give me extensive help for the horrible trauma this app gave me. i still have nightmates from it. since i deleted the app i get messages from the trump number sending me death threats. i got one message from barron telling me he’s in trouble and needs to be saved. it got so bad i had to get a new a new phone. i am now in debt and living in a cardboard box on the street. ive tried to sell the trump merch the app automatically bought for me but no one wants to buy it and makes fun of me for supporting bunker boy. when i try to tell them my story and that i don’t support him they spit on me and take my money. this has been a traumatic experience and i wish i could rate this app 0 stars. i would not suggest this app to the person i hate the most which happens to be that orange man in that oval office. do NOT get this app.
